Reasoning: The paper discusses multimedia encryption schemes and the use of cryptography to protect sensitive information, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also mentions the use of various multimedia technologies, which suggests that it may also fall under the category of multimedia (cs.MM). The paper discusses the efficiency, flexibility, and security of the encryption schemes, which suggests that it may also fall under the categories of information theory (cs.IT) and cybernetics (cs.CY). Finally, the paper discusses the need for appropriate protection of digital documents, which suggests that it may also fall under the category of software engineering (cs.SE).
